00:19:40.410 --> 00:19:47.350
&gt;&gt; Why did you think
it was a bad idea

00:19:47.350 --> 00:19:52.810
for all your family
to live in one house?

00:19:52.810 --> 00:19:54.650
&gt;&gt; Meg Medina: Because
in real life,

00:19:54.650 --> 00:19:59.860
because I knew how my family was
and everybody had an opinion.

00:19:59.860 --> 00:20:03.500
And everybody had,
everybody could raise me.

00:20:03.500 --> 00:20:07.380
So it wasn't my parents, my
mother wasn't the only one

00:20:07.380 --> 00:20:10.760
who could tell me to go to bed
or not eat this or do that,

00:20:10.760 --> 00:20:14.560
everybody, so it was going
to be like having six

00:20:14.560 --> 00:20:17.850
or seven moms and dads on me.

00:20:17.850 --> 00:20:20.580
And that felt hard for me.

00:20:20.580 --> 00:20:24.290
