was hard, it taught all

00:20:32.940 --> 00:20:39.530
of us this way of being
generous to each other

00:20:39.530 --> 00:20:42.730
and patient with each other.

00:20:42.730 --> 00:20:46.340
There were some really
sad days together

00:20:46.340 --> 00:20:51.170
and then there were also some
really happy days together.

00:20:51.170 --> 00:20:55.650
And I wouldn't trade it, I
wouldn't do it differently.

